		  a given workstation.
 
	       2. This property	will only affect the operation of the 
		  object when the VIEWSTYLE property is	set to 
		  $VIEWREPORT style.
 
 
	   HOVERTIME=dnumnvar		   (See	PLBEQU.INC)
 
	     This property sets the time for automatic hot-track selection
